        "text": "",
        "text_original": "うん、百蓮も持ったよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_formation_in_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_formation_in_2",
        "category": "formation",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "右腕、今なら大丈夫。任せて。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_formation_in_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_formation_select",
        "category": "formation",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生がそうしたいなら……従うよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_formation_select.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_gachaget",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "こうして海に来たんだもの……みんなと忘れられない思い出を作りたいんだ。先生も、一緒に……付き合ってくれる？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_gachaget.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_growup_1",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "これで……右腕の封印が1つ解けた。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_growup_2",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "そっか。私にもまだ伸びしろがあったんだね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_growup_3",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "黄昏から取り戻した、私の力……見せてあげる。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_growup_4",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "つぼみが開いたような感じがする。ありがとう、先生のおかげだよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_growup_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_1_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "これ……どう、かな？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_1_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_1_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "思ったより似合う水着が見つからなくて……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_1_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_2_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "白を選んだ理由……？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_2_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_2_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "これが良いって、みんなに言われたから……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_2_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_3_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "スキンケアの秘訣？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_3_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_3_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "別に特別なことをしているわけじゃないんだけど……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_3_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_3_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あ。もしかしたら焼き鳥のおかげかも？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_3_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_4_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "大切なものは失ってから気づくって、よく言うよね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_4_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_4_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "私もそうだった。だから――",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_4_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_4_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "もう手放さない。絶対に。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_4_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "右腕が黄昏に呑まれてから、私は誰かの手にすがることを忘れてしまった。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "だからいつも一人で考えて、全部自分で解決しようとしてた。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "……だけど、今は違う。先生とみんながいるから。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_lobby_5_4",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "これからも……よろしくね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_lobby_5_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_login_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "おかえり、先生。今日もお役に立てたらいいな。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_login_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_login_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あ……待ってたよ。海に行くんだよね？もう着替えておいたよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_login_2.ogg"
      },
      {
