        "text": "",
        "text_original": "",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_5",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_5.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_6_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_6_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_memoriallobby_6_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_memoriallobby_6_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_1",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "雪が解けたら、春が訪れるように……。荒れ果てた私の心にも、芽吹きの時が来たみたい。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_2",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "やっぱり優しいね。私も、いつか先生みたいになりたいな。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_3",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "いつも信じてくれてありがとう。……先生のこと、頼りにしてるよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_relationship_up_4",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "美人なこと以外、特に取り柄がないんだけど……先生のそばにいても……いいかな？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_relationship_up_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "私が冬に生まれたのには意味があるんだと思う。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "冬の厳しさを越えて、麗らかな日の下に咲く花のように……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "私もいつか、咲き誇りたいんだ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_player_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "そばにいるだけで安心できる人がいるんだ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_player_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_player_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "今日はその人の誕生日なんだって。だから思い出に残るように、この格好でお祝いするね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_player_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_birthday_player_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "お誕生日おめでとう、先生。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_birthday_player_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_halloween_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "今日みたいな日に水着……。私はただ水着を着ただけなのかな？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_halloween_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_halloween_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "え、違う？コスプレの世界って奥深いんだね……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_halloween_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_newyear_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あけましておめでとう、先生。お正月くらいは明るい話がいいよね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_newyear_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_newyear_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "だから形からではあるんだけど……明るい気分になれる格好にしてみたんだ……",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_newyear_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_xmas_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "寒さには強いほうだよ。ほら、今も水着だけど平気。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E7%A8%9C%20%E5%90%8D%E8%8D%89/%E6%B3%B3%E8%A3%85/jp/ch0303_season_xmas_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "ch0303_season_xmas_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あ……今日は赤い服の方が……良かった……？",
